last_episode_to_air.name: The Labyrinth
last_episode_to_air.overview: Election day arrives. Daniela and her staff prepare for the worst. JJ stalks Monsanto and witnesses a terrible murder. Verónica gives JJ an ultimatum.

name: Wild District
overview: After surrendering to Bogotá police, an ex-guerrilla avoids prison by working undercover to investigate a ruthless enforcer of government corruption.

episodes.name: Coercion
episodes.overview: After giving himself up to officials, a former guerrilla reunites with his long-lost family and accepts an undercover mission in exchange for immunity.

episodes.name: Infiltration
episodes.overview: To get close to Apache, Jhon seeks work from a team of mercenaries, who test him ruthlessly. Prosecutor León forges an alliance with a TV reporter.

episodes.name: Intimidation
episodes.overview: Mario has his first day at his new school. Jhon starts working for Total Security, but Apache's right-hand man Cabeto is mistrustful and tails him.

episodes.name: Bribery
episodes.overview: Apache is sent to bribe Prosecutor León. A child is abducted from Mario's school. Jhon and Verónica try going on a different kind of date.

episodes.name: Theft
episodes.overview: Agent Duque sends Jhon to a bank to take photos of documents that reveal who's behind a shady firm's accounts. Mario gets in trouble with the law.

episodes.name: Raid
episodes.overview: The cops raid the construction firm and Total Security. Jhon gets a tip on the kidnapping, and later runs into a familiar face. A betrayal stuns Mario.

episodes.name: Disappointment
episodes.overview: Provoked by a schoolmate, Mario lashes out. Jhon accepts a potentially life-changing mission from Apache, and goes alone to face Aníbal and his men.

episodes.name: Betrayal
episodes.overview: After suffering a serious setback, Prosecutor León is offered a lifeline. Agent Duque traces Apache's intel on the kidnapping to a walled estate.

episodes.name: Execution
episodes.overview: A police press conference about the kidnapping makes Apache suspicious of Jhon, who preps for a risky job. Mario gets a package from the U.S. Embassy.

episodes.name: Judgement
episodes.overview: Caldera unveils an audacious plan designed to expose Apache's powerful associates. Aníbal visits Jhon's home. Julie's fate is revealed.

episodes.name: The District
episodes.overview: JJ is still working as a hitman but also trying to assimilate into civilian life. Daniela's campaign for president is at a crossroads.

episodes.name: The Pit
episodes.overview: JJ goes to buy missiles in Venezuela and ends up in jail, tortured. After going after her rivals at the presidential debate, Daniela's numbers improve.

episodes.name: The Trail
episodes.overview: Daniela's campaign counters a personal attack and she makes it to the election finals. JJ experiences horrors crossing the Venezuelan-Colombian border.

episodes.name: The Hood
episodes.overview: Apache is back and down on his luck, but then he unwittingly hears about the Venezuelan missiles and convinces Chacho and China to do one last job.

episodes.name: The Beehive
episodes.overview: Mario, JJ's son, comes for an unexpected visit, just as JJ is struggling and contacted by Apache about the missiles. The past catches up with Daniela.

episodes.name: The Mousetrap
episodes.overview: Ramón, Daniela's husband, asks for a divorce and custody of their daughter at a crucial moment. In order to save JJ, Apache takes a drastic step.

episodes.name: The Streets
episodes.overview: Daniela goes to Caldera for help, no longer trusting Carmen. JJ and Giselle pair up to investigate a pair of murders. Stef quits in disgust.

episodes.name: The Alley
episodes.overview: Monsanto and JJ beat the pulp out of each other. Carmen sets Daniela up with corrupt right-wingers but she sees through her scheme, as does Caldera.

episodes.name: The Slum
episodes.overview: There's a crisis at home but JJ can't deal with it because Caldera sends him to retrieve the missing missile. Daniela gathers info to denounce everyone.

episodes.name: The Labyrinth
episodes.overview: Election day arrives. Daniela and her staff prepare for the worst. JJ stalks Monsanto and witnesses a terrible murder. Verónica gives JJ an ultimatum.
